 planning, self-management, and effective time management, while also being able to adapt to new environments and maintain discipline in a remote work setup.", "citations": {"f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_256892267": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"To succeed as a digital nomad, one needs to possess skills such as financial planning, self-management, and effective time management, as well as be able to work efficiently and have a creative outlet.\"", "citations": {"f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_256892267": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Succeeding as a digital nomad requires a combination of personal management skills, such as financial planning and effective time management, and the right technological tools, including reliable remote desktop software, to address connectivity issues and maintain productivity in different environments.\"", "citations": {"b67cd69f-4c83-4193-99ab-2cc0767b6bfd_37536649": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Succeeding as a digital nomad requires a combination of financial planning, self-management, virtual communication, and effective time management skills, as exemplified by the story of Daniella Pashuk, who has been working remotely in 20 countries over 5 years.\"", "citations": {"a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641": 80.0}}, {"text": "Succeeding as a digital nomad requires careful financial planning, self-management, and cooperation, as well as effective time management and virtual communication skills, due to the unpredictability of income and expenses.", "citations": {"a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641": 80.0}}, {"text": "Japan will launch its digital nomad visa in March 2024.", "citations": {"ec9e942a-2b47-4552-9825-4e206606823c_696735006": 100.0}}, {"text": "Japan will launch its digital nomad visa at the end of March 2024, allowing applications from 49 countries, including Taiwan.", "citations": {"b67b7441-6604-4229-82d6-e410e0419e0b_1051067344": 80.0}}, {"text": "Japan is launching its digital nomad visa program in March, requir