ination for digital nomads.", "citations": {"b67b7441-6604-4229-82d6-e410e0419e0b_1051067344": 80.0}}, {"text": "Japan is introducing a digital nomad visa program, opening applications to 49 countries including Taiwan, starting at the end of March.", "citations": {"b67b7441-6604-4229-82d6-e410e0419e0b_1051067344": 80.0}}, {"text": "Japan is introducing a digital nomad visa program for foreign high-level technicians and technology engineers, allowing them to stay in the country for up to six months while working remotely.", "citations": {"15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219": 80.0}}, {"text": "Japan is launching a digital nomad visa program to attract remote workers and boost economic growth.", "citations": {"15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219": 80.0}}, {"text": "Japan's digital nomad visa requires a minimum annual income of 10 million yen.", "citations": {"b67b7441-6604-4229-82d6-e410e0419e0b_1051067344": 100.0}}, {"text": "The minimum annual income required for Japan's digital nomad visa is 10 million yen.", "citations": {"15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219": 100.0}}, {"text": "Japan's digital nomad visa requires a minimum annual income of 10 million yen.", "citations": {"ec9e942a-2b47-4552-9825-4e206606823c_696735006": 100.0}}, {"text": "The minimum annual income required for Japan's digital nomad visa is 10 million Japanese Yen, and applicants must also have private health insurance coverage.", "citations": {"ec9e942a-2b47-4552-9825-4e206606823c_696735006": 100.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads require skills such as self-discipline, time management, and strategic thinking to successfully manage their work and life while traveling.", "citations": {"eb9bb425-89ea-45e2-9b52-ed2a0f921fe9_132088186": 80.0}}, {"text": "A digital nomad lifestyle requires skills such as self-discipline and time management to balance work and life while working remotely.", "citations": {"eb9bb425-89ea-45e2-9b52-ed2a0f921fe9_132088186": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"A