vilizations. Despite being disproven by early astronomers, the theory has seen a resurgence in the modern era, with online groups and public figures supporting it.", "citations": {"f61994b0-dc34-40d6-a1e2-a7f66b22774b_548175167": 80.0}}, {"text": "The flat earth theory is a conspiracy theory that rejects scientific evidence of the Earth's shape, despite historical observations and measurements that prove the Earth is not flat.", "citations": {"f61994b0-dc34-40d6-a1e2-a7f66b22774b_548175167": 80.0}}, {"text": "The flat earth theory is a conspiracy theory that rejects scientific evidence of Earth's shape, promoted by individuals and organizations such as Samuel Rowbotham and William Carpenter, and has resurfaced in modern times mixed with other conspiracy theories.", "citations": {"f61994b0-dc34-40d6-a1e2-a7f66b22774b_548175167": 80.0}}, {"text": "The flat earth theory is a conspiracy theory that rejects scientific evidence of Earth's shape, and has been transformed from ignorance of science into a conspiracy theory that has been imported into various parts of the world.", "citations": {"f61994b0-dc34-40d6-a1e2-a7f66b22774b_548175167": 80.0}}, {"text": "Muslim scholars, specifically Al-Ma'mun astronomers, disproved the flat Earth theory by measuring the circumference of the Earth using the height of the polar star.", "citations": {"f61994b0-dc34-40d6-a1e2-a7f66b22774b_548175167": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Abu Rayhan Al-Biruni, a Muslim scholar, disproved the flat Earth theory around a thousand years ago by calculating the Earth's circumference using triangulation.\"", "citations": {"f61994b0-dc34-40d6-a1e2-a7f66b22774b_548175167": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Muslim scholars disproved the flat Earth theory over a thousand years ago, using experimental scientific methods and collecting astronomical data from various cultures.\"", "citations": {"f61994b0-dc34-40d6-a1e2-a7f66b22774b_548175167": 80.0}}, {"text": "Muslim scholars played a significant role in disproving the flat Earth theory over a thousand years ago, contributing to the understanding of the earth's sphericity.", "citations": {"f61994b0-dc34-40d6-a1e2-a7f66b22774b_548175167": 80.0}}, {"text": "Al-Biruni calculated the Earth's circumference using a trigonometric equation based on triangulation, measuring the angle of the sun's descent from a mountain.", "citations": {"f61994b0-dc34-40d6-a1e2-a7f66b22774b_548175167": 90.0}}, {"text": "Neil deGrasse Tyson, a renowned scientist, responded to Kyrie Irving's Flat Earth claim in a logical manner.", "citations": {"f6eb21b5-aefb-47b5-a467-cf0ff072bc84_615722827": 80.0}}, {"text": "People in modern society, particularly those attracted to the flat Earth movement, often seek simplistic explanations and are drawn to primitive ideas.", "citations": {"6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320": 80.0}}, {"text": "People in modern society often seek simplistic explanations for complex issues, which can be attributed to the desire for easy-to-understand and reproducible information.", "citations": {"4f5c11c2-2047-4883-9ce2-c925423b4a7b_264796898": 80.0}}, {"text": "People often seek simplistic explanations in modern society because they prefer quick and easy answers over complex and nuanced ones.", "citations": {"4f5c11c2-2047-4883-9ce2-c925423b4a7b_264796898": 80.0}}, {"text": "People in modern society often seek simplistic explanations for complex phenomena, which can contribute to the appeal of movements like flat Earth theory.", "citations": {"4f5c11c2-2047-4883-9ce2-c925423b4a7b_264796898": 80.0}}], "references": ["bb504df7-75f4-4d5f-a1c5-be1652e12594_703346419", "4f5c11c2-2047-4883-9ce2-c925423b4a7b_264796898", "f61994b0-dc34-40d6-a1e2-a7f66b22774b_548175167", "4796c046-7fb6-4cd7-a2ed-03923fed0941_640399993", "f6eb21b5-aefb-47b5-a467-cf0ff072bc84_615722827", "622d24ae-9987-4fda-a84c-bb94203f6c65_1060788103", "6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320", "00310f0f-f13a-484e-a6fe-9e53d1ab632d_486305547"]}
