om critics.", "citations": {"458f78da-4fd3-48c7-8c6a-4d32ba5efffa_645465952": 80.0}}, {"text": "Disney's animated movie \"Wish\" is scheduled to be released on November 22, 2023.", "citations": {"800e6594-4a58-4429-a918-25f13f8757aa_119137286": 100.0}}, {"text": "The live-action remake of Disney's Hercules is being produced by Joe and Anthony Russo, with Guy Ritchie set to direct.", "citations": {"c5f26e63-75b5-48b1-9501-c8ee23be61f2_694539873": 100.0}}, {"text": "Joe Russo and Anthony Russo are producing the live-action remake of Disney's Hercules due to their strong emotional connection to the original movie.", "citations": {"c5f26e63-75b5-48b1-9501-c8ee23be61f2_694539873": 80.0}}, {"text": "The Little Mermaid, Dumbo, and Pinocchio are Disney live-action remakes that have generated backlash, with The Little Mermaid facing criticism for its casting choice and Dumbo and Pinocchio likely facing backlash due to their deviations from the original stories.", "citations": {"08bf5561-f112-47d8-ae82-2041a9b4fc15_814052845": 80.0}}, {"text": "The live-action remakes of Disney classics, such as The Little Mermaid, Dumbo, and Pinocchio, have generated backlash due to their struggles in balancing authenticity with modern adaptations.", "citations": {"08bf5561-f112-47d8-ae82-2041a9b4fc15_814052845": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"The Little Mermaid live-action remake has received mixed reviews, with some critics praising the performances while others find it to be an unoriginal remake. This, along with other remakes like Dumbo and Pinocchio, suggests that not all Disney live-action remakes have been well-received by audiences.\"", "citations": {"08bf5561-f112-47d8-ae82-2041a9b4fc15_814052845": 80.0}}, {"text": "The Little Mermaid live-action remake has been a financial and cultural success, but has also faced backlash, including racist criticism, despite its positive impact on representation.", "citations": {"84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498": 80.0}}, {"text": "The Little Me