 equality by implementing inclusive policies and strategies, such as signing the Women's Empowerment Principles and setting diversity goals, to increase the number of women in leadership positions and challenge traditional gender barriers.", "citations": {"65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"The construction industry can promote gender equality by implementing inclusive policies, challenging biases and stereotypes, and providing opportunities for female employees to develop their professional qualities, as seen in the example of a company that successfully overcame prejudices against female leaders.\"", "citations": {"65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178": 80.0}}, {"text": "The construction industry can promote gender equality by addressing systemic issues, challenging biases, and providing equal opportunities for women.", "citations": {"c40b5c1c-6e7a-45f6-a314-adcf276acb8c_663217418": 80.0}}, {"text": "Amelia Walker-Ross is an example of a woman who succeeded in a male-dominated field, overcoming pushback and unwanted opinions to pursue her passion for working on vehicles.", "citations": {"b4382681-f199-43dc-a190-ef39b5bf9a5d_476864776": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Amelia Walker-Ross is an example of a woman succeeding in a male-dominated field, such as the construction industry, where she works on trucks and helps others learn and grow.\"", "citations": {"b4382681-f199-43dc-a190-ef39b5bf9a5d_476864776": 80.0}}, {"text": "Amelia Walker-Ross is an example of a woman succeeding in a male-dominated field, demonstrating that with determination and support, women can overcome obstacles and excel in traditionally male-dominated roles.", "citations": {"b4382681-f199-43dc-a190-ef39b5bf9a5d_476864776": 80.0}}, {"text": "Irene Naliaka is an example of a woman succeeding in a male-dominated field, having worked as a professional driver for ten years and becoming proficient in her job, demonstrating that women can excel in traditionally male-dominated roles.", "citations": {"14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281": 80.0}}, {"text": "Irene Naliaka is an example of a woman who succeeded in a challenging situation, finding a way to support her family after her husband's accident and overcoming initial reservations to achieve her goals.", "citations": {"14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281": 80.0}}, {"text": "Companies can attract women construction workers by creating a more inclusive hiring process and work environment.", "citations": {"37e0b781-4c2a-44c1-bed6-e2c232792ed9_107068371": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Companies can attract women construction workers by offering paid training programs and creating an equal employment environment, as evidenced by the success of training programs like the one at SLCC.\"", "citations": {"5db3cd35-e9aa-45e4-92a6-f53a64c446d3_904794769": 80.0}}, {"text": "Companies can attract women construction workers by offering paid training programs and fostering an equal employment environment, as seen in the Meralco Linecrew Training Program which promotes gender diversity and inclusion in the field of electrical linework.", "citations": {"42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_682318363": 80.0}}, {"text": "Companies can attract women construction workers by offering paid training programs and creating an equal employment environment, which can help break down traditional gender barriers and promote career growth opportunities.", "citations": {"42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_682318363": 80.0}}, {"text": "Companies can attract women construction workers by providing paid training and equal employment opportunities, helping to break down traditional gender barriers and promote diversity in the industry.", "citations": {"42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_682318363": 80.0}}, {"text": "Promoting gender equality in the construction industry aims to increase female representation and achieve sustainable social development by breaking down traditional gender barriers and providing opportunities for women to succeed in male-dominated roles.", "citations": {"5db3cd35-e9aa-45e4-92a6-f53a64c446d3_904794769": 80.0}}, {"text": "Promoting gender equality in the construction industry aims to increase female representation and achieve sustainable social development by breaking down traditional gender barriers and creating a welcoming environment for women.", "citations": {"b4382681-f199-43dc-a190-ef39b5bf9a5d_476864776": 80.0}}, {"text": "Promoting gender equality in the construction industry aims to increase female representation and achieve sustainable social development, as seen in examples of women breaking into male-dominated fields like offshore wind power.", "citations": {"061641d6-49c2-4b0c-ac1e-001c86b80a9e_89871675": 80.0}}, {"text": "Promoting gender equality in the construction industry aims to increase female representation and achieve sustainable social development, as seen in the example of a female trainee who overcame challenges to become a wind technician.", "citations": {"061641d6-49c2-4b0c-ac1e-001c86b80a9e_89871675": 80.0}}, {"text": "Promoting gender equality in the construction industry aims to increase female representation and achieve sustainable social development by breaking down traditional gender barriers and providing opportunities for women to excel in male-dominated roles.", "citations": {"65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178": 80.0}}, {"text": "The percentage of truck drivers who are women is 7.9% as of 2021, indicating an increase from 4.9% in 1999.", "citations": {"f8c8c06e-76b0-48f9-a66b-758fd08d0ac4_246084211": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"The trucking industry is still male-dominated, but there is a slight increase in female drivers, with females making up less than 10% of commercial drivers license holders nationally.\"", "citations": {"f8122819-7f94-4b55-86f1-db6e58439897_133703253": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Women can excel in male-dominated roles such as crane operation by possessing qualities like confidence, perseverance, determination, and a strong mindset, as exemplified by successful women leaders in similar industries.\"", "citations": {"37e0b781-4c2a-44c1-bed6-e2c232792ed9_107068371": 80.0}}, {"text": "Women can excel in male-dominated roles such as crane operation by possessing qualities like perseverance, dedication, and a strong mindset, and by being part of a supportive work environment that provides opportunities for growth and development.", "citations": {"42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_682318363": 80.0}}, {"text": "Women can excel in male-dominated roles by possessing confidence, perseverance, determination, and a strong mindset, as exemplified by Cornilla Johnson's experience training to drive a Class A vehicle.", "citations": {"f8c8c06e-76b0-48f9-a66b-758fd08d0ac4_246084211": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Women can excel in male-dominated roles by possessing confidence, perseverance, determination, and a strong mindset, as exemplified by Chen Pei-fen's story, and by being eager to break through and make a change in their careers.\"", "citations": {"5a54db3a-0b44-4679-9cca-4285568ae817_488233346": 80.0}}, {"text": "Women can excel in male-dominated roles like crane operation by having confidence, perseverance, and the right mindset, and by not being limited by their past, gender, or age.", "citations": {"5a54db3a-0b44-4679-9cca-4285568ae817_488233346": 80.0}}, {"text": "To attract women workers, companies can offer training programs, which will help break down traditional gender barriers and create a more diverse and inclusive work environment.", "citations": {"37e0b781-4c2a-44c1-bed6-e2c232792ed9_107068371": 80.0}}, {"text": "Companies can attract women workers by offering training programs, promoting gender diversity and inclusion, and providing opportunities for skill development and knowledge acquisition.", "citations": {"42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_682318363": 80.0}}, {"text": "Companies can attract women workers by offering training programs, as seen in Meralco's introduction of female linecrew trainees into the MLTP, providing equal opportunities for both men and women.", "citations": {"42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_682318363": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Companies can attract women workers by offering training programs and career growth opportunities, as seen in Meralco's approach to promoting gender equality and diversity.\"", "citations": {"42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_682318363": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Companies can offer training programs to attract women workers, as seen in Meralco's successful program, which not only produces skilled professionals but also fosters a culture of equality and empowerment.\"", "citations": {"42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_682318363": 80.0}}, {"text": "Construction companies can incentivize women to join by offering higher pay, as it is a motivator for some women in the industry who value the financial rewards and the opportunity to make a positive impact.", "citations": {"5db3cd35-e9aa-45e4-92a6-f53a64c446d3_904794769": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Offering higher pay can be an effective way to incentivize women to join the construction industry, as seen in the example of Li Rui, a tower crane driver who earns a competitive monthly income.\"", "citations": {"fa814205-0346-442b-87c5-93059583ffff_953125432": 80.0}}, {"text": "Educational programs and vocational training can support women in construction by providing them with the necessary skills and preparation to succeed in male-dominated fields.", "citations": {"5db3cd35-e9aa-45e4-92a6-f53a64c446d3_904794769": 80.0}}, {"text": "Educational programs and vocational training, such as the 25-week program at SLCC, can support women in construction by providing them with the necessary skills and training to excel in the industry.", "citations": {"5db3cd35-e9aa-45e4-92a6-f53a64c446d3_904794769": 80.0}}, {"text": "Educational programs and vocational training can support women in construction by providing them with the necessary skills and experience to succeed in the field, as evidenced by the success of the SLCC program.", "citations": {"5db3cd35-e9aa-45e4-92a6-f53a64c446d3_904794769": 80.0}}, {"text": "Educational programs and vocational training, such as Meralco's Linecrew Training Program, can support women in construction by providing them with the necessary skills and knowledge to excel in the field.", "citations": {"42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_682318363": 80.0}}, {"text": "Educational programs and vocational training can support women in construction by providing them with the necessary skills and opportunities to excel in their roles.", "citations": {"42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_682318363": 80.0}}, {"text": "Women can succeed in construction and maritime industries by working together as a team and being open to new knowledge and opportunities, with the support of their company.", "citations": {"65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178": 80.0}}, {"text": "Women can succeed in construction and maritime industries by being part of a cohesive team and having the desire to learn and develop, which helps break down traditional gender barriers.", "citations": {"f5dde440-7c4c-4eaf-99cd-8aabd52b7901_186077154": 80.0}}, {"text": "Companies can support women workers by implementing policies such as improved maternity leave, male decree programs, and compensation for differences in family income, allowing women to continue their career growth and balance work and family responsibilities.", "citations": {"65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178": 80.0}}, {"text": "Having role models can help encourage more women to join the construction field by inspiring and showing them that they too can succeed in the industry.", "citations": {"37e0b781-4c2a-44c1-bed6-e2c232792ed9_107068371": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Role models, such as Jewel Everett, the first woman lineworker at LUS Fiber, can help encourage more women to join the construction field by providing inspiration and breaking down traditional gender barriers.\"", "citations": {"5db3cd35-e9aa-45e4-92a6-f53a64c446d3_904794769": 80.0}}, {"text": "Role models like Jewel Everett can inspire and encourage more women to join the construction field, helping to break down traditional gender barriers and promote greater gender equality and diversity.", "citations": {"5db3cd35-e9aa-45e4-92a6-f53a64c446d3_904794769": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Role models can play a significant role in encouraging women to join the construction field by breaking down traditional gender barriers and showing that success is achievable.\"", "citations": {"061641d6-49c2-4b0c-ac1e-001c86b80a9e_89871675": 80.0}}, {"text": "The presence of role models can help encourage more women to join the construction field by empowering them to pursue their aspirations.", "citations": {"9b95a346-03b3-49ba-86e4-adf7e644b438_910039464": 80.0}}, {"text": "Companies can support women in male-dominated industries by providing resources and support, such as training programs, to help them succeed and break down traditional gender barriers.", "citations": {"42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_682318363": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Companies can promote gender equality by offering equal training and opportunities, as exemplified by Meralco's initiative to include female linecrew trainees in their program.\"", "citations": {"42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_682318363": 80.0}}], "references": ["c40b5c1c-6e7a-45f6-a314-adcf276acb8c_663217418", "5a54db3a-0b44-4679-9cca-4285568ae817_488233346", "65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178", "061641d6-49c2-4b0c-ac1e-001c86b80a9e_89871675", "9b95a346-03b3-49ba-86e4-adf7e644b438_910039464", "f8c8c06e-76b0-48f9-a66b-758fd08d0ac4_246084211", "42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_682318363", "14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281", "b4382681-f199-43dc-a190-ef39b5bf9a5d_476864776", "f5dde440-7c4c-4eaf-99cd-8aabd52b7901_186077154", "5db3cd35-e9aa-45e4-92a6-f53a64c446d3_904794769",