fd1-e5448e2b55a6_1005984929": 80.0}}, {"text": "Salmon feed during farming may include additives such as fishmeal, fish oil, and insect-based ingredients, with insects, mold, and algae being considered as potential future alternatives.", "citations": {"8c32d1ae-e169-4582-9fd1-e5448e2b55a6_1005984929": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"The additives used in salmon feed during farming likely include fishmeal and fish oil, as well as other land-grown ingredients such as wheat flour, soybean meal, and vegetable oil, although the exact composition may vary depending on the type of fish and its stage of growth.\"", "citations": {"ced34f0a-144c-4eec-afab-98de204f3bfe_726039735": 70.0}}, {"text": "\"Insect-based ingredients, such as mealworms, are being used as additives in salmon feed, potentially replacing traditional fishmeal and fish oil.\"", "citations": {"8c32d1ae-e169-4582-9fd1-e5448e2b55a6_1005984929": 60.0}}, {"text": "Insect meal is used as an additive to replace fish meal in salmon feed, as it provides a sustainable alternative to wild-caught fish.", "citations": {"8c32d1ae-e169-4582-9fd1-e5448e2b55a6_1005984929": 80.0}}, {"text": "Insect meal is used as an additive in salmon feed to replace fish meal.", "citations": {"8c32d1ae-e169-4582-9fd1-e5448e2b55a6_1005984929": 80.0}}, {"text": "Antibiotics are often used in salmon feed but are being replaced due to health concerns and environmental impacts.", "citations": {"39b66508-c08e-45cc-aca1-ebcd84856d91_226266469": 80.0}}, {"text": "The country where feed additives are managed is Taiwan, as inferred from the context of the source document.", "citations": {"71711d57-11ff-4e5d-a397-a88062ea3ef3_934508136": 60.00000000000001}}, {"text": "Traditional single species fish farms use antibiotics and additives.", "citations": {"39b66508-c08e-45cc-aca1-ebcd84856d91_226266469": 80.0}}, {"text": "Antibiotics and additives are used in traditional single species fish farms to maintain a healthy fish-stock.", "citations": {"39b66508-c08e-45cc-aca1-ebcd84856d91_226266469": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Traditional single species fish farms use antibiotics and additives, but some farms are starting to use probiotics like Lactic Acid Bacillus B4 to improve fish growth and immunity.\"", "citations": {"206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Traditional single species fish farms use antibiotics and additives, but natural, non-antibiotic solutions are also available as an alternative.\"", "citations": {"5c561ad7-437a-42fa-ae5a-dbee6279a512_142193131": 80.0}}, {"text": "Adding amino acids to feed is done to enhance nutritional value, which is crucial for the robust growth of fish, as implied by the need for a balanced nutrient supply.", "citations": {"08513efb-f585-43cf-80c9-6a72d864444a_35299894": 80.0}}, {"text": "Amino acids are added to feed to enhance its nutritional value by supporting cell growth and immune system development.", "citations": {"09cbaa0c-5e42-4814-a1a1-3e28d939b1c4_429459585": 80.0}}, {"text": "The addition of amino acids to feed is intended to increase its nutritional value, and the use of feed additives in general aims to maximize the absorption of nutrients and enhance productivity.", "citations": {"09cbaa0c-5e42-4814-a1a1-3e28d939b1c4_429459585": 70.0}}, {"text": "Replacing antibiotics with natural ingredients in salmon feed aims to produce healthier fish by using probiotics that improve fish growth and immunity.", "citations": {"206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288": 80.0}}, {"text": "The goal of replacing antibiotics with natural ingredients in salmon feed is to produce healthier fish by improving their growth and immunity.", "citations": {"206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288": 80.0}}, {"text": "Replacing antibiotics with natural ingredients in salmon feed can lead to healthier fish, as seen in an experiment where yogurt feed resulted in faster growth and no disease.", "citations": {"206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288": 80.0}}, {"text": "Replacing antibiotics with natural ingredients in salmon feed can lead to healthier fish, reduced breeding risk, and lower costs.", "citations": {"206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288": 80.0}}, {"text": "The name of the methane-reducing feed additive is Bovaer, which is approved for marketing in the European Union for dairy cows.", "citations": {"19a72dbf-3566-40b4-ae9b-f102cbfc2f92_400224801": 80.0}}, {"text": "The name of the methane-reducing feed additive is Bovaer, which has been shown to reduce enteric methane emissions in cows.", "citations": {"19a72dbf-3566-40b4-ae9b-f102cbfc2f92_400224801": 80.0}}, {"text": "The name of the methane-reducing feed additive is Bovaer.", "citations": {"19a72dbf-3566-40b4-ae9b-f102cbfc2f92_400224801": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Omega 3 is a beneficial nutrient for heart health in farmed salmon, specifically the fatty acids EPA and DHA.\"", "citations": {"e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371": 100.0}}, {"text": "Omega 3, specifically EPA and DHA, is beneficial for heart health in farmed salmon.", "citations": {"e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371": 80.0}}, {"text": "Omega 3 is a beneficial nutrient for heart health found in farmed salmon.", "citations": {"e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371": 80.0}}, {"text": "Lactobacillus B4 is a probiotic used in fish feed to enhance growth and improve resistance to pathogens.", "citations": {"206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288": 90.0}}, {"text": "Lactobacillus B4 is a probiotic used in fish feed to enhance growth and immunity.", "citations": {"206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288": 80.0}}, {"text": "The probiotic Lactobacillus B4 is used in fish feed to enhance growth.", "citations": {"206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288": 80.0}}, {"text": "Lactobacillus B4 is a probiotic used in fish feed to enhance growth and improve health.", "citations": {"206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288": 80.0}}, {"text": "The types of Omega 3 fatty acids found in farmed salmon are EPA and DHA.", "citations": {"e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371": 100.0}}, {"text": "Farmed salmon contains EPA and DHA, two types of Omega 3 fatty acids that are beneficial for heart health and thinking skills.", "citations": {"e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371": 100.0}}, {"text": "Insect-based proteins are used as additives in salmon feed in France, as suggested by the potential future of fish feed.", "citations": {"8c32d1ae-e169-4582-9fd1-e5448e2b55a6_1005984929": 80.0}}, {"text": "The new salmon feed includes essential amino acids, which are crucial for animal protein production and immune body formation.", "citations": {"09cbaa0c-5e42-4814-a1a1-3e28d939b1c4_429459585": 80.0}}], "references": ["8c32d1ae-e169-4582-9fd1-e5448e2b55a6_1005984929", "19a72dbf-3566-40b4-ae9b-f102cbfc2f92_400224801", "71711d57-11ff-4e5d-a397-a88062ea3ef3_934508136", "09cbaa0c-5e42-4814-a1a1-3e28d939b1c4_429459585", "08513efb-f585-43cf-80c9-6a72d864444a_35299894", "39b66508-c08e-45cc-aca1-ebcd84856d91_226266469", "206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288", "5c561ad7-437a-42fa-ae5a-dbee6279a512_142193131", "e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371", "ced34f0a-144c-4eec-afab-98de204f3bfe_726039735"]}
