4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 80.0}}, {"text": "The India-Russia relationship is strong and steady, based on strategic convergence and mutual benefit, with cooperation in areas such as trade, energy, and investments.", "citations": {"9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"President Putin aims to maintain a privileged strategic partnership with India, as seen in the recent communication between PM Modi and Putin, highlighting their commitment to regular dialogue on various issues under the India-Russia Special and Privileged Strategic Partnership.\"", "citations": {"18a87794-ba47-4d33-a1b5-bf97307dd44b_224507163": 80.0}}, {"text": "Prime Minister Modi and President Putin discussed the Ukraine crisis, with Putin briefing Modi on developments and Modi willing to resolve the matter peacefully.", "citations": {"9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 80.0}}, {"text": "Prime Minister Modi and President Putin discussed the global food market, the Ukraine war, and BRICS during their telephone conversation, with a focus on further developing economic ties between Russia and India.", "citations": {"fa329c8a-ec3f-4c25-92cd-e38bcfe14cf6_276748561": 80.0}}, {"text": "Prime Minister Modi and President Putin discussed the Ukraine war, with Modi appealing to Putin to end the war, stating that there is no solution on the battlefield.", "citations": {"614b97d3-73a1-4056-8643-bb4a28b93b74_623335570": 80.0}}, {"text": "Prime Minister Modi and President Putin last met in person in 2019, and the current meeting is their first in-person meeting since then, implying the current year is also a year they met in person.", "citations": {"d749981a-0acd-425d-8652-51e8701d6755_959152834": 100.0}}, {"text": "Prime Minister Modi and President Putin met in person at the 21st India-Russia Summit, with their last meeting likely occurring in 2022, given the annual nature of the summit and the lack of information about a meeting in 2023 or later.", "citations": {"21ed01ca-807c-44ff-a30d-2f665ef65e50_383211104": 80.0}}, {"text": "The target trade volume between India and Russia by 2025 is $30 billion.", "citations": {"ea97d66c-aef3-451a-98a6-59f0c7b366c3_225244470": 100.0}}, {"text": "The target trade volume between India and Russia by 2025 is $30 billion.", "citations": {"21ed01ca-807c-44ff-a30d-2f665ef65e50_383211104": 80.0}}, {"text": "The target trade volume between India and Russia by 2025 is $30 billion.", "citations": {"bd315e2c-88b4-4024-a5e6-3a31bfa14029_791557688": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Modi and Putin are expected to discuss regional and global security issues, including the situation in Afghanistan, during their meeting.\"", "citations": {"21ed01ca-807c-44ff-a30d-2f665ef65e50_383211104": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Modi and Putin's meeting will discuss regional and global security, trade, and other topics, with a focus on strengthening the India-Russia relationship amidst regional security concerns and global power dynamics.\"", "citations": {"3b61be6d-6469-4de5-b1a1-7836856db935_401996737": 80.0}}, {"text": "Modi and Putin are expected to discuss regional and global security, as well as bilateral trade and economic cooperation, during their meeting.", "citations": {"3b61be6d-6469-4de5-b1a1-7836856db935_401996737": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Modi and Putin are likely to discuss regional and global security, including Russia's special military operation in Ukraine, as well as the COVID-19 pandemic, during their meeting, as they work to strengthen the strategic partnership between Russia and India.\"", "citations": {"fa329c8a-ec3f-4c25-92cd-e38bcfe14cf6_276748561": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"India has agreed to procure military equipment, including nuclear-powered submarines, S-400, and AK-203, from Russia, as part of their defense cooperation, highlighting India's strategic independence and efforts to balance its relationships with major powers.\"", "citations": {"18a87794-ba47-4d33-a1b5-bf97307dd44b_224507163": 80.0}}, {"text": "India has agreed to procure military equipment, including the S-400 missile system, from Russia, which may trigger US sanctions under CAATSA.", "citations": {"21ed01ca-807c-44ff-a30d-2f665ef65e50_383211104": 80.0}}, {"text": "The total trade value between India and Russia last year was over $50 billion or 65 billion dollars, indicating an expansion in trade between the two countries.", "citations": {"9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 80.0}}, {"text": "The total trade value between India and Russia last year was over $50 billion.", "citations": {"9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 80.0}}, {"text": "The total trade value between India and Russia last year was over $50 billion, with India importing around $60 billion from Russia and Russia importing less than 10% of that amount from India.", "citations": {"a8edad1b-d157-466a-9ba5-057e6b4399d9_841501382": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Narendra Modi and Vladimir Putin are likely to hold talks in Moscow, Russia, as Putin has invited Modi to visit Russia in 2024.\"", "citations": {"9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Narendra Modi is visiting Russia to meet with Vladimir Putin, signaling strong ties between India and Russia. The exact location of their talks is Moscow, Russia.\"", "citations": {"a8edad1b-d157-466a-9ba5-057e6b4399d9_841501382": 80.0}}, {"text": "Narendra Modi and Vladimir Putin will likely hold talks in Moscow, Russia, as part of Modi's visit to the country.", "citations": {"a8edad1b-d157-466a-9ba5-057e6b4399d9_841501382": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Narendra Modi and Vladimir Putin held talks in New Delhi.\"", "citations": {"21ed01ca-807c-44ff-a30d-2f665ef65e50_383211104": 80.0}}, {"text": "Narendra Modi and Vladimir Putin will hold talks in India, as Putin is scheduled to visit India on December 6.", "citations": {"24a3f54d-6cb6-4848-ac50-fd92a4ffd58e_995732433": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Narendra Modi and Vladimir Putin have emphasized expanding India-Russia cooperation, reaffirming their 'special and privileged strategic partnership' and signing multiple agreements to strengthen bilateral relations.\"", "citations": {"bd315e2c-88b4-4024-a5e6-3a31bfa14029_791557688": 90.0}}, {"text": "\"Narendra Modi and Vladimir Putin have emphasized expanding India-Russia cooperation in various areas, including political, strategic, economic, and security cooperation, reaffirming their commitment to the Special and Outstanding Strategic Partnership.\"", "citations": {"b955247a-98fd-4d7a-bc42-c0683adb7b44_448016859": 90.0}}, {"text": "\"Narendra Modi and Vladimir Putin have emphasized expanding India-Russia cooperation, with a focus on trade, investment, and connectivity in the Eurasian space and Indian and Pacific Oceans.\"", "citations": {"792e3539-8d3e-404d-925f-2d2e14af8105_958547503": 80.0}}, {"text": "Narendra Modi and Vladimir Putin have emphasized expanding India-Russia cooperation, particularly in the context of building a 'Greater Eurasian space'.", "citations": {"792e3539-8d3e-404d-925f-2d2e14af8105_958547503": 80.0}}, {"text": "The leaders who have emphasized expanding India-Russia cooperation are Narendra Modi and Vladimir Putin, as evidenced by their attempted summit meetings and the frequent meetings between their representatives, such as Jaishankar and Lavrov.", "citations": {"9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 80.0}}, {"text": "Indian Prime Minister Narendra Modi has been invited to visit Russia in 2024 by President Putin.", "citations": {"9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 80.0}}, {"text": "Modi and Putin emphasized cooperation in defense and space programs, with Russia considering India a great power and time-tested friend, and the two nations developing high technologies together.", "citations": {"d749981a-0acd-425d-8652-51e8701d6755_959152834": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Modi and Putin have emphasized cooperation in defense and space programs, with a focus on jointly producing military equipment and strengthening military ties.\"", "citations": {"05ddbc47-8544-4bb7-8449-143ff74e846a_947839176": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Modi and Putin emphasized cooperation in defense and space programs, including joint production of weaponry and procurement of defense systems.\"", "citations": {"21ed01ca-807c-44ff-a30d-2f665ef65e50_383211104": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Modi and Putin have emphasized cooperation in defense and space programs, with a focus on joint ventures and agreements for the production of military equipment, including rifles, submarines, and fighter aircraft.\"", "citations": {"21ed01ca-807c-44ff-a30d-2f665ef65e50_383211104": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Modi and Putin have emphasized cooperation in defense and space programs, signing agreements such as the 2021-2031 Military Technology Cooperation Agreement and the space technology protection agreement, to deepen relations and counterbalance US influence in the Indo-Pacific region.\"", "citations": {"bd315e2c-88b4-4024-a5e6-3a31bfa14029_791557688": 80.0}}, {"text": "Russia's praise of India for not joining US and EU sanctions is related to the Ukraine war, which has led to increased cooperation and trade between the two nations.", "citations": {"792e3539-8d3e-404d-925f-2d2e14af8105_958547503": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Russia has praised India for not joining US and EU sanctions due to the Ukraine war, marking a significant event in the evolving India-Russia relationship under Modi and Putin.\"", "citations": {"9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430": 80.0}}, {"text": "\"Russia praised India for not joining US and EU sanctions over the Ukraine war, as India has maintained a neutral stance and continued to engage in trade with Russia.\"", "citations": {"05ddbc47-8544-4bb7-8449-143ff74e846a_947839176": 80.0}}, {"text": "The event that led to Russia's praise of India was India's decision not to join US and EU sanctions, specifically its refusal to condemn Russia's invasion of Ukraine and its increased energy trade with Moscow.", "cita